         ConsequenceResult overload, no ProduceDetails*/CalculateDepthZeroDamage/
         FindHighestDepthZeroPercentDamage (CSV + f_inverse). The tuple ComputeDamage, FindOccType/
         FindOccTypeIndex, AddRules, ResetIndexTracking, and the four LastWSP index fields are kept
         verbatim; see that file's header for the full patch rationale. patched/Structure.cs needs
