         *.cs file under the project directory, including patched/, the same way
         patched/CurveMetaData.cs and patched/GraphicalDistribution.cs are already picked up. -->
    <!-- Task Phase4T3: AggregatedConsequencesBinned's real source pulls in System.Xml.Linq
