         GetGraphicalStageFrequency, the GetWSE-driven half of
         GetHydraulicDatasetInFloatsWithProbabilities, ToXML, and
         AllStagesIncreaseWithDecreasingProbability - all need RasMapperLib/Geospatial.GDALAssist/
         HEC.FDA.Model.Spatial/hydraulics.enums/Interfaces/paireddata/structures/System.Xml.Linq,
         none reachable from this subset-compiled project (same rationale as patched/Structure.cs's
         dropped ctors). Same auto-pickup as the patched/ files above, no explicit Compile Include. -->
